      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for [Model Name] finished in a sophisticated Slate Grey Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable companion and remains in solid mechanical and aesthetic shape. The exterior paint holds a high-gloss finish, though upon close inspection, you will find a few typical stone chips on the hood and a minor door ding on the passenger side consistent with careful street parking. The alloy wheels are clean with no significant curb rash. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and features black leather upholstery that remains firm and supportive; there is some light entry wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, but the carpets and headliner are pristine. All power windows, the sunroof, and the dual-zone climate control function perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is dry and runs quietly, with a consistent maintenance history including a recent fluid service and a battery replacement last winter. The car tracks straight and the suspension feels tight over bumps. It currently sits on a set of all-season tires with plenty of life left. This is a dependable, honest vehicle ready for its next owner.",
